column2: "Bravo, Kiku-hime! Your martial arts are truly a work of art...!"
"Greetings, my friend! I'm so glad to see you."
"There's no need for concern. These injuries were sustained during Kiku-hime's training, they are irreplaceable gifts."
"I cherish everything I receive from my beloved children, even the bruises."
"She's speaking to you. Pleased to meet you, I am Kiku-hime. Meeting with you is a great honor."
"Kiku-hime is courteous and refined, and cares greatly for her companions!"
"She's prone to worrying, but very affectionate. When I am tired, she provides a tender massage. Would you be so kind, Kiku-hime?"
"Ada! Adadadada!"
"You needn't focus so unrelentingly on my abdomen... adadada!"
"...Ghah! My... how effective a solar plexus massage is! My body is covered in a cold sweat...!"
"I've been tenderized by her tenderness! Well, my friend? Is she not the most kindhearted?"
"It looked like she was hurting you."
"She really likes you."
"It was a massage! It has relaxed my muscles, removed my exhaustion, and reforged my body."
"And I love her. Because I can tell how deeply she cares for me."
"To be able to experience this overflowing affection in a deluge of blows, I am truly blessed!"
"The way she flows from one strike to the next... So elegant! So beautiful! Truly, she is a martial artiste!"
"Hahaha, see how modest she is. She's saying, your praise is too much. It was nothing worthy of such acclamation."
"What do you say, my friend? Would you like to witness Kiku-hime's beauteous barrage firstha- ghoh!"
"Wait, not yet... idadada! Calm dow- adadadada!"

"Such eagerness! But wait a secondndndndndnd!
I'll die... gwoahuh!"
